description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene (Actinomyces bovis farcinicus; Actinomyces farcinicus; Bacillus farcinicus; Bacillus nocardi; Bacterium nocardi; Cladothrix farcinica; Discomyces farcinicus; Oospora farcinica; Streptothrix farcini bovis; Streptothrix farcinica; Streptothrix nocardii.  Use when strain, subtype, isolate, etc. is unspecified, or when different from all specified ones in Gene.).
